_Pa’al_ of קדש: The shoresh קדש has a [[_pa’al_]] form, which follows [[_pa’al_ forms for regular shorushim|regular conjugations]] for the _pa’al_. קדש in the _pa’al_ can mean:
- to be or become pure
- to be or become sacred/holy/connected
- to be or become separated or designated for a special purpose
